子Meghan接受Oprah Winfrey的專訪播出後，親皇室的英國傳媒反擊，ITV早晨節目《英國早晨》（Good Morning Britain）今天9日節目，播出跟Meghan父親Thomas Markle的訪問。有關內容部份片段，可在該節目的Twitter觀看，ITV網站亦有文字報導版。<br />\n<br />\n無論是在Oprah的專訪，抑或之前的傳聞，Meghan一向不滿，自己下嫁Harry前，父親接受英國小報訪問，而且在訪問出街前還要向她謊稱沒有向傳媒交談，亦不滿父親把二人的私人書信公開給傳媒。<br />\n<br />\nThomas在GMB的專訪中說，他已向女兒道歉了過百次，繼續接受傳媒訪問，只是因為女兒不肯跟他說話。他強調，就算父女不和，但作為父親，仍然深愛著女兒。<br />\n<br />\n在Oprah的專訪，最有機會引發政治後遺症的言論，是Meghan指有皇室成員擔心她的兒子日後膚色會否太黑，暗指英國皇室存在種族歧視。<br />\n<br />\n但她的父親Thomas為英國皇室辯護，說洛杉磯或者加州可能存在種族主義，但認為英國皇室和英國人不是種族主義者，那個「嬰兒日後皮膚會深色嗎？」可能只是無聊愚蠢問題而已，是很簡單的一件事。<br />\n<br />\n他又批評女兒和女婿，在菲臘親王仍在醫院養病時，容許訪問播出，並不恰當，應該體諒一下英女皇的心情。<br />\n<br />\nOprah的專訪，在美國由CBS購買播放權，在星期日7號晚上播放，英國的播放權由ITV奪得，在星期一8日晚上播出，較美國遲了四分三天。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，GMB其中一名主持、亦即這次Meghan父親訪問其中一位進行者，是英美兩國著名主持人Piers Morgan，他是強烈支持皇室和保守派的人士，在Oprah的訪問前後，已不斷抨擊Meghan及丈夫接受訪問。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:03:01.000Z","msg":"佢老竇都頂自己個女唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:18:20.000Z","msg":"根據左癌邏輯Meghan 老豆係咪種族主義者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b66ec54d4ce887fcc10bfb4d3ee539d5879269","tid":2440132,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"我都認為哈利最終原因係錢<br />\n查理斯可能cut 9晒佢d資金來源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n王冠有一幕就係講愛華頓八世<br />\n返黎參加細佬既葬禮<br />\n然後伊利莎白老母話佢害撚死佢細佬佐治六世<br />\n因為愛德華八世明明就係國王.但不愛江山愛美人<br />\n讓位俾佢細佬.走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n故事講到伊利莎白老母cut 9埋大伯個資金來源<br />\n佢向瑪麗皇后投訴.之後丘吉爾要愛華德說服<br />\n伊利沙白即係依家是頭婆住白金漢宮.d仔女個姓要起溫莎<br />\n而唔可以係跟老公果邊紅黎傾條件<br />\n<br />\n喂呢套野咁出名.無理由左膠無睇到嫁<br />\n佢地無唸返呢一幕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9fc5f21d8b7692e067b49766508cb2c1300be4","tid":2440132,"uid":221490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:51:56.000Z","msg":"好煩呀 根本係一個咩都奶唔到ga怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f568d29b57e149cc6c1b07e39154ed0be611034f","tid":2440132,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eabf12597276c1ab17ba67ae4e611121cff4bcfd","tid":2440132,"uid":30384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0b87011ea96558fdfcf85fe1b6203b3eb9717dc8","tid":2440132,"uid":173207,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"1e17f53377f321e0b743b5a8febde9aa71a75d32","tid":2440132,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T17:51:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-_7kjFJyLJI8/YEc-1BCQYiI/AAAAAAAAH9o/GMO9gLLU59M-SZPZifXkL4KuKQo_DNjsQCLcBGAsYHQ/s500/meghanfather_210309_itv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-_7kjFJyLJI8%2FYEc-1BCQYiI%2FAAAAAAAAH9o%2FGMO9gLLU59M-SZPZifXkL4KuKQo_DNjsQCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs500%2Fmeghanfather_210309_itv.jpg&h=7e3d7ee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2021/03/meghan.html?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F03%2Fmeghan.html%3F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=8b8c0725\" target=\"_blank\">https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2021/03/meghan.html?</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gmb/status/1369204980058570752?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgmb%2Fstatus%2F1369204980058570752%3Fs%3D21&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=8f985e2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgmb%2Fstatus%2F1369204980058570752%3Fs%3D21&h=512a6d08\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gmb/status/136