r />\n日日喺度洗大家腦(大家可以google下九成新聞無論咩人結婚都一定係女方「下嫁」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n已經係其中一樣令到社會越嚟越女尊男卑嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2346e1be4f9a1835db4f01655d968317f6d3ed3c","tid":2440132,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:38:37.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：曬太陽會變黑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你唔好種族歧視啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :  想買件黑色衫（琴）污糟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你唔好種族歧視啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：點解有白頭髮架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你唔好種族歧視啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我啲屎近排好黑色<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你唔好種族歧視啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我屌撚你啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你係種族歧視者"}]}